                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190421-24-defend279 t18190421-24-punish148"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>. Aged 34.</p>
               <p>SMEED - <rs id="t18190421-24-verdict149" type="verdictDescription">
